metadata.name: Leveling Up Heroes - PFP #1
metadata.description: Leveling Up Heroes is an NFT Project focused on connecting & collaborating with driven people. Created by a public & proven team that has helped grow Uber, Amazon, and Airbnb. Leveling Up heroes PFP is a collection of 12,345 hand-drawn NFTs. By owning one, not only do you get a beautiful and unique hero, but you will also have access to utilities provided by top entrepreneurs like Eric Siu and Neil Patel.
